      <li><article class="PostIntro declSearch smaller ">
    <a class="PostIntro-a" href="https://www.contrepoints.org/2017/01/18/278198-grace-de-chelsea-manning-veut-obama">
      <div class="PostIntro-imgDiv" data-url="https://www.contrepoints.org/2017/01/18/278198-grace-de-chelsea-manning-veut-obama" data-title="Grâce de Chelsea Manning : que veut Obama ?">
                <span class="PostIntro-imgSpan" style="background-image: url('https://www.contrepoints.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/9632091382_0129e62722_z.jpg')"></span>
              </div>
      <div class="PostIntro-titleContainer">
        <h2 class="PostIntro-title">Grâce de Chelsea Manning : que veut Obama ?</h2>
              </div>
      <div class="PostIntro-textContainer">
        <div class="PostIntro-categ">Libertés publiques</div>
        <p class="PostIntro-text ">À quelques jours de la passation de pouvoir, Barack Obama a décidé d&#039;accorder sa clémence à Chelsea Manning qui avait écopé de 35 ans de prison pour avoir transmis des documents confidentiels à Wikileaks.</p>
      </div>
    </a>
        <div class="PostIntro-meta">
      <time class="PostIntro-time " datetime="2017-01-18T13:11:44Z">le 18 jan. 2017</time> par
      <span class="PostIntro-author"><a href="https://www.contrepoints.org/author/f-mas">Frédéric Mas </a></span>
    </div>
        </article></li><li><article class="PostIntro declSearch smaller ">
    <a class="PostIntro-a" href="https://www.contrepoints.org/2017/01/18/278193-socialisme-ennemi-cest-finance">
      <div class="PostIntro-imgDiv" data-url="https://www.contrepoints.org/2017/01/18/278193-socialisme-ennemi-cest-finance" data-title="Socialisme : mon ennemi, c&#039;est la finance ?">
                <span class="PostIntro-imgSpan" style="background-image: url('https://www.contrepoints.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/finances-rené-le-honzec.png')"></span>
              </div>
      <div class="PostIntro-titleContainer">
        <h2 class="PostIntro-title">Socialisme : mon ennemi, c'est la finance ?</h2>
              </div>
      <div class="PostIntro-textContainer">
        <div class="PostIntro-categ">Caricatures</div>
